    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                <date>Aug 8th/52</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Your favor of<lb/>
                <date><sic>may</sic></date> was duly received—and should<lb/> have replied to it—but
                was prevented<lb/> from doing by sickness in my family—<lb/>and business—and knowing
                that—I was<lb/> shortly going to visit this city, I <sic>defered</sic><lb/> writing
                    <sic>untill</sic> my arrival here,<lb/> have received pay from the
                following<lb/> persons in advance for your Occident</p>
            <table cols="2" rows="9">
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>Moses Bumberger</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>3.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><persName>Simons</persName> &amp; <persName>Walker</persName></cell>
                    <cell>3.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>L Kramer</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>3.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>Emanuel David</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>3.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>Leobold Foltz</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>3.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><persName>L Landah</persName> one quarter</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline"> .75<lb/></hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>$15.75</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Exchange on $16</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline"> 16<lb/></hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Balance</cell>
                    <cell>$15.59</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p><persName>L Landah</persName> does not wish your work longer<lb/> than 3 months for
                which he has paid me.<lb/> the balance of your subscribers were not<lb/> willing to
                pay in advance. You will please<lb/> call on <persName>Messrs Wolf Arnold &amp;
                    Co</persName> and<lb/> receive the above amount $15.60 which</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>I have left with them to pay you</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">with my best respects I am</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Yours Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Benjamin Emanuel</persName>
            </p>
            <p>The post office in <placeName>Memphis</placeName> say that<lb/> when any work is
                refused to be taken<lb/> out of the office—they do not reserve<lb/> them, but throw
                them away</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">B E</persName>
            </p>
            <p>the Occident does not arrive regular<lb/> to all subscribers</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>Editor of the Occident</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Pa</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
